<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 14:07:20 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>在英国，“反犹太主义和对犹太人的消极态度已成为主流、普遍存在”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-02-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-britain-negative-attitudes-about-jewish-people-have-become-mainstream/0000018d-b1d0-d9b4-a19f-f9d3f9aa0000</link><description>在英国创纪录的反犹太主义袭击一年之后，社区安全信托基金的戴夫·里奇指出，激增是在哈马斯袭击以色列之后立即开始的，而不是在以色列对加沙进行报复期间。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 13:29:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-02-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-britain-negative-attitudes-about-jewish-people-have-become-mainstream/0000018d-b1d0-d9b4-a19f-f9d3f9aa0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列南部恐怖袭击中枪手造成两人死亡、四人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/two-killed-four-wounded-in-terror-attack-in-southern-israel/0000018d-b1d9-de6d-a1fd-b9dd18c30000</link><description>警方称，枪手驾车抵达十字路口，并向附近的一个公交车站开枪。他被一名开车经过袭击地点的武装平民开枪打死</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 12:27:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/two-killed-four-wounded-in-terror-attack-in-southern-israel/0000018d-b1d9-de6d-a1fd-b9dd18c30000</guid></item><item><title>据报道埃及在加沙边境修建围墙以应对大规模逃亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/egypt-constructing-walled-off-area-on-gaza-border-as-contingency-for-mass-exodus/0000018d-b0f8-de6d-a1fd-b9fcd2920000</link><description>开源情报显示，埃及一直在建设一个坚固的“缓冲区”，一旦加沙人大规模逃往埃及，该缓冲区可以为数万名巴勒斯坦人提供庇护</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 09:15:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/egypt-constructing-walled-off-area-on-gaza-border-as-contingency-for-mass-exodus/0000018d-b0f8-de6d-a1fd-b9fcd2920000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡：以色列拒绝国际社会就巴勒斯坦最终地位解决方案发出的命令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-israel-rejects-intl-diktats-on-final-status-solution-with-the-palestinians/0000018d-b09b-d070-a7fd-f6bf371c0000</link><description>以色列总理在回应《华盛顿邮报》有关实施两国解决方案计划的报道时表示，单方面承认巴勒斯坦国将是“恐怖活动的巨大奖励”</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 06:44:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-israel-rejects-intl-diktats-on-final-status-solution-with-the-palestinians/0000018d-b09b-d070-a7fd-f6bf371c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙南部的战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-combat-in-southern-gaza/0000018d-b08a-de6d-a1fd-b9cee2160000</link><description>参谋军士。哈巴是过去一天在加沙地带战斗中丧生的第二名伞兵</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 06:23:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-combat-in-southern-gaza/0000018d-b08a-de6d-a1fd-b9cee2160000</guid></item><item><title>官员预计以色列和哈马斯将在下个月达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.premium/officials-expect-hostage-deal-between-israel-and-hamas-over-the-next-month/0000018d-ae62-dc8c-a3df-fe772ff80000</link><description>一位参与谈判的消息人士表示，实施协议的“理想时间”是在 3 月 10 日开始的斋月期间</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 04:05:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.premium/officials-expect-hostage-deal-between-israel-and-hamas-over-the-next-month/0000018d-ae62-dc8c-a3df-fe772ff80000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨政党的官员相信内塔尼亚胡已准备好结束紧急政府伙伴关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.premium/gantz-party-officials-believe-netanyahu-is-ready-to-end-partnership/0000018d-adda-da6e-af9f-addb2b6a0000</link><description>甘茨领导的民族团结党内的消息人士认为，总理的目标是启动他较为温和的战时内阁伙伴，以强硬反对他的右翼基地的人质交易。一名官员表示，内塔尼亚胡“希望每个人都谈论政治，这样就没有人会谈论人质”</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 04:05:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.premium/gantz-party-officials-believe-netanyahu-is-ready-to-end-partnership/0000018d-adda-da6e-af9f-addb2b6a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的“全面胜利”只是一个政治口号，而不是一个现实目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-total-victory-is-a-political-slogan-not-a-realistic-goal/0000018d-adae-d070-a7fd-ffae37c80000</link><description>尽管以色列军队的救援行动令人印象深刻，并且明显逼近辛瓦尔，但哈马斯的失败并未迫在眉睫。 ■ 斋月前东耶路撒冷和约旦河西岸的紧张局势加剧，有可能爆发第三次起义。要不是 134 名人质仍在加沙，就成了每天的头条新闻</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 04:04:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-total-victory-is-a-political-slogan-not-a-realistic-goal/0000018d-adae-d070-a7fd-ffae37c80000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡针对人质的影响力运动是宣传大师班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-influence-campaign-against-the-hostages-is-a-master-class-in-propaganda/0000018d-ae87-de6d-a1fd-afc7cc750000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的“全面胜利”影响力运动与针对人质家属的地下运动交织在一起，当以色列官员加班加点地谈判释放人质的协议时，总理正在破坏他们的进展，以迎合他的极右翼根据</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 04:00:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-influence-campaign-against-the-hostages-is-a-master-class-in-propaganda/0000018d-ae87-de6d-a1fd-afc7cc750000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在汗尤尼斯纳赛尔医院拘留哈马斯恐怖分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article-live/after-40-minute-call-with-biden-netanyahu-rejects-intl-diktats-on-palestinian-state/0000018d-aff4-d070-a7fd-fff430710000</link><description>周四，两名以色列伞兵在加沙地带丧生 ■ 内塔尼亚胡警告单方面承认巴勒斯坦国将是“恐怖主义的巨大奖励” ■ 拜登重申美国反对拉法行动，除非平民得到保护 ■ 周四，数千人抗议内塔尼亚胡政府，呼吁以色列人质获释 ■ 北部城市基亚特什莫纳 (Kiryat Shmona) 遭到来自黎巴嫩的 25 枚火箭弹袭击</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 03:37:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article-live/after-40-minute-call-with-biden-netanyahu-rejects-intl-diktats-on-palestinian-state/0000018d-aff4-d070-a7fd-fff430710000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列人往往会忘记并快速前进。我想记住我从战争中学到的东西”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-02-16/ty-article/.highlight/israelis-tend-to-forget-quickly-i-want-to-remember-what-ive-learned-from-the-war/0000018d-afb0-de6d-a1fd-aff4992a0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一位年轻的企业主因加沙战争而重新思考她的优先事项，一位系统工程师在访问台湾时得出了有关中国的结论</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 02:39:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-02-16/ty-article/.highlight/israelis-tend-to-forget-quickly-i-want-to-remember-what-ive-learned-from-the-war/0000018d-afb0-de6d-a1fd-aff4992a0000</guid></item><item><title>她离开了正统世界。这就是为什么她担心留在那里的孙女</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/she-left-the-haredi-world-heres-why-she-worries-for-her-granddaughters-who-remain-there/0000018d-af63-de6d-a1fd-afe729270000</link><description>她的前夫发誓保持沉默，对女儿们永无休止的哀悼，以及她选择的“自由世界”和她留下的极端正统世界之间的生活。作家朱迪思·罗特姆访谈</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 02:10:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/she-left-the-haredi-world-heres-why-she-worries-for-her-granddaughters-who-remain-there/0000018d-af63-de6d-a1fd-afe729270000</guid></item><item><title>“定居者是对的”：即将卸任的领导人表示基布兹运动应该脱离左派</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/settlers-are-right-the-kibbutz-movement-should-break-away-from-the-left-leader-says/0000018d-ad9e-da6e-af9f-ad9f0a270000</link><description>以色列北部和南部的基布兹都受到战争的严重打击，这提醒公众他们为国家做出的贡献，而不仅仅是在国防方面。但基布兹运动即将离任的务实负责人表示，为了继续蓬勃发展，他们需要不惜一切代价</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 00:47:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/settlers-are-right-the-kibbutz-movement-should-break-away-from-the-left-leader-says/0000018d-ad9e-da6e-af9f-ad9f0a270000</guid></item><item><title>尼尔奥兹基布兹宣布先前被认为在加沙被扣为人质的居民死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/kibbutz-nir-oz-announces-death-of-resident-previously-thought-to-be-held-hostage-in-gaza/0000018d-ae57-d070-a7fd-fe775b040000</link><description>11 月，在以色列和哈马斯之间的人质交易中，亚伊尔·雅科夫 (Yair Yaakov) 的两个儿子雅吉尔 (Yagil) 和奥尔 (Or) 与其女友梅拉夫·塔尔 (Merav Tal) 一起被释放</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 20:22:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/kibbutz-nir-oz-announces-death-of-resident-previously-thought-to-be-held-hostage-in-gaza/0000018d-ae57-d070-a7fd-fe775b040000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队公布在加沙地带战斗中丧生的士兵姓名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/israeli-army-releases-name-of-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-combat/0000018d-ae28-d070-a7fd-fe2c4e630000</link><description>两名伞兵旅士兵和一名军官在这起事件中受重伤，导致 20 岁的中士丧生。罗特姆·萨哈尔·哈达尔</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 19:41:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/israeli-army-releases-name-of-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-combat/0000018d-ae28-d070-a7fd-fe2c4e630000</guid></item><item><title>用我们的鲜血跳舞的以色列政客并不是极右怪胎。他们是决策者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/far-right-freaks-theyre-the-decision-makers/0000018d-ade0-dc8c-a3df-fff53fa70000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 19:25:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/far-right-freaks-theyre-the-decision-makers/0000018d-ade0-dc8c-a3df-fff53fa70000</guid></item><item><title>为什么拜登现在要公布他对以色列和巴勒斯坦人的愿景，以及其中的内容</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.premium/why-biden-is-unveiling-his-vision-for-israel-and-the-palestinians-now/0000018d-ad33-da6e-af9f-ad3b2d840000</link><description>拜登主义的长期目标是建立一个非军事化的巴勒斯坦国，10 月 7 日之后，以色列人并不容易接受拜登主义。但替代方案最终可能会更糟糕</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 19:14:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.premium/why-biden-is-unveiling-his-vision-for-israel-and-the-palestinians-now/0000018d-ad33-da6e-af9f-ad3b2d840000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的内容 – 第 132 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-132/0000018d-ae00-da6e-af9f-ae091e1d0000</link><description>据报道，美国和几个阿拉伯国家旨在提出以色列-巴勒斯坦和平计划，包括建立巴勒斯坦国的时间表 ■ 在总理命令以色列代表团不要返回开罗进行停火谈判后，中央情报局局长会见了内塔尼亚胡 ■ 以色列国防军正在汗尤尼斯 (Khan Yunis) 的纳赛尔医院 (Nasser Hospital) 进行手术 ■ 战争结束 132 天后，您需要了解以下信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 18:42:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-132/0000018d-ae00-da6e-af9f-ae091e1d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列：目前尚无证据表明哈马斯在加沙纳赛尔医院扣押人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/israeli-army-raids-south-gaza-hospital-searching-for-bodies-of-hostages/0000018d-ada9-dc8c-a3df-ffbdd6670000</link><description>以色列国防军开始袭击加沙南部最大的医疗机构汗尤尼斯的纳赛尔医院。军方表示，在收到人质被关押在医院的“可靠情报”后，他们撤离了医院，他们的尸体可能还留在医院里。现场报道称以色列军队挖掘了临时坟墓</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 17:55:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/israeli-army-raids-south-gaza-hospital-searching-for-bodies-of-hostages/0000018d-ada9-dc8c-a3df-ffbdd6670000</guid></item><item><title>“可怕的强烈反应”：以色列海外民主党董事会因对加沙战争的反应而退出该组织</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/terrifying-backlash-democrats-abroad-israel-board-quits-group-over-response-to-gaza-war/0000018d-accd-d9c8-a58f-becd1f5b0000</link><description>海外民主党是一个致力于动员居住在美国境外的美国选民的组织，该组织的领导层在 10 月 7 日之后未能真正承认损失对其内部人员的影响，该组织在以色列的成员表示，他们感到不安，并对这九人的遭遇表示同情。董事会——但并没有被吓倒</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 16:22:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/terrifying-backlash-democrats-abroad-israel-board-quits-group-over-response-to-gaza-war/0000018d-accd-d9c8-a58f-becd1f5b0000</guid></item></channel></rss>